
<html dir="rtl" lang="ar"><head><title>حساب جديد</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.rtl.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
    body { font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; background: #f4f7f6; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
    .auth-card { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); width: 100%; max-width: 400px; }
    .btn-primary { border-radius: 50px; padding: 10px; font-weight: bold; background: #1a2a6c; border: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body><div class="auth-card text-center">
    <h3>إنشاء حساب جديد ✨</h3><br>
    <form action="/signup" method="POST">
        <input type="text" name="username" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="اسمك بالكامل" required>
        <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="الإيميل" required>
        <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="كلمة السر" required>
        <button class="btn btn-primary w-100 mb-3">إنشاء حساب</button>
    </form>
    <a href="/login" class="text-decoration-none">عندك حساب؟ ادخل من هنا</a>
</div></body></html>